title.rendered: Briemarpak Alcohol Wipes, Skin Cleansing Swabs, 200 Pack

content.rendered:
Briemarpak Alcohol Swabs are 70% Isopropyl Non-woven Alcohol swabs suitable as an antibacterial wipe as well as a multipurpose cleaner. Briemar Nominees Pty Ltd is a proudly Australian owned and operated family company, and licensed to produced Sterile an Non Sterile Pharmaceuticals.

FEATURES:

  • 70% Isopropyl Alcohol
  • Non-woven swab
  • Individually wrapped
  • 56 x 30mm in size
  • 200 pieces per box
